<item>
            <title>[HTTPCLIENT-287] Setting CONNECTION_TIMEOUT and SO_TIMEOUT on a per-method basis</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HTTPCLIENT-287</link>
                <project id="12310360" key="HTTPCLIENT">HttpComponents HttpClient</project>
                        <description>The capability of setting connection timeout and socket timeout on a per-method&lt;br/&gt;
basis should be provided. This would enable different threads, sharing the same&lt;br/&gt;
HttpClient, to set different timeouts for their methods executions.</description>
                <environment>Operating System: other&lt;br/&gt;
Platform: Other</environment>
